HEADWORD: Olympus
<hw>Olympus</hw> <pos>prop. n.</pos> <def>A mountain in Northeastern
Greece; -- it was believed by ancient Greeks to be the dwelling place of
the gods.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> Mount Olympus, Mt. Olympus, Olimbos.</syn>⟦br⟧
